  "text": "The Cuieiras reserve has an area of 22,735 ha and is located about 60 km north of Manaus, embedded in a vast area of pristine rainforest [CITATION_1] . It is accessed via ZF-2, an unpaved road running west from the main BR-174 Manaus-to-Caracas highway.",
